request.description: Performs aggregations on a document set within the given bounding box. Basic call, with no optional parameters.
Performs aggregations on a document set within the given bounding box. Using all optional parameters; ISO-8601 date range.
Performs aggregations on a document set within the given bounding box. Grouped aggregation of cardinality and terms; "now" date range.
Aggregation query with arbitrary geometry (instead of bounding box).
